pass out devices
Everyone log in (with devices, connect via the website)


Photo Event:
 - Admin starts photo event
 - Clients take pictures and upload
 - Photos come into Admin view, then admin triggers processing
 - Admin sends mosaic to clients, open mosaic
 
Send Message:
- Admin writes message, then sends
- Clients get message on screen (show a few screens)

Contest:
- Admin writes winner message, then sends
- One Client gets winning message on screen

Show Editor
- Create Show
- Load Audio File
- Add a few events
- Save

Run a Live Show
- Admin picks a show and queues it up
- Show Client getting queued
- Admin starts the show
- Show Side-by-side clients and admin running show
